<p>
<li><b>The geometric thickness of low degree graphs.</b><br>
<a href="//www2.latech.edu/~duncan/">C. Duncan</a>,
D. Eppstein, and
<a href="//www.cs.arizona.edu/~kobourov/">S. Kobourov</a>.<br>
<a href="//arxiv.org/abs/cs.CG/0312056">arXiv:cs.CG/0312056</a>.<br>
